- ğŸ›  **Customizable**: Configurable sync intervals, file filtering, and more.

## ğŸš€ Quick Start

1. **Install ClaudeSync:**
```shell
pip install claudesync
```

2. **Log in to your Claude.ai account:**
```shell
claudesync api login claude.ai
```

3. **Start syncing:**
```shell
claudesync sync
```

